body:
Hello Dr. Harri James,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I apologize if it seemed like I was being silent, but I assure you that I am interested in learning more about the fund. Could you please provide me with some additional information? What exactly is this fund and how did my name become associated with it?

Best wishes,
Joelle
